OL,3,CClaim that Manchester Arena bombing
OL,4,Cwas staged is absurd, judge rules
OL,6,FHowever, in a ruling on Thursday,
OL,7,FJudge Richard Davison ruled in favour
OL,8,Fof the pair and said that without this
OL,9,Fearly decision, Mr Hall would "use the
OL,10,Ftrial as a vehicle to advance and test
OL,11,Fhis staged attack hypothesis".
OL,13,FJudge Davison said: "Suffice it to say
OL,14,Fthat, although his beliefs may be
OL,15,Fgenuinely held, his theory that the
OL,16,FManchester bombing was an operation
OL,17,Fstaged by government agencies in which
OL,18,Fno one was genuinely killed or injured
OL,19,Fis absurd and fantastical and it
OL,20,Fprovides no basis to rebut the
OL,21,Fconviction."
